ities and rescue teams to use simple tools such as spades and ropes to search for survivors."SOURCES: Reuters, South China Morning Posthttps://www.reuters.com/article/us-indonesia-mine-collapse/indonesia-says-scores-missing-after-illegal-gold-mine-collapses-idUSKCN1QG02Mhttps://www.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/2187844/indonesia-says-t-three-killed-another-60-feared-buried***]]></description>
